msgid "# triton.language.insert_slice"
msgstr "# triton.language.insert_slice"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/insert_slice.md:2
msgid "## 1. OP 概述"
msgstr "## 1. OP Overview"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/insert_slice.md:4
msgid ""
"简介：将一个张量（子张量）插入到另一个张量的指定位置，即将一个张量按照操作指定的偏移量、大小和步幅参数插入到另一个张量中。\n"
"原型：\n"
msgstr ""
"Introduction: Insert a tensor (sub-tensor) into a specified position of another tensor, that is, insert one tensor into another tensor according to the offset, size, and stride parameters specified by the operation.\n"
"Prototype:\n"

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/insert_slice.md:6
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"triton.language.insert_slice(\n"
"    ful,\n"
"    sub,\n"
"    offsets,\n"
"    sizes,\n"
"    strides,\n"
"    _builder=None,\n"
"    _generator=None\n"
") -> tensor\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/insert_slice.md:8
msgid "## 2. OP 规格"
msgstr "## 2. OP Specifications"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/insert_slice.md:10
msgid "### 2.1 参数说明"
msgstr "### 2.1 Parameter Description"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/insert_slice.md:12
msgid ""
"| 参数名           | 类型                | 说明                                                             |\n"
"| ------------- | ----------------- | -------------------------------------------------------------- |\n"
"| `ful`        | `tensor`          | 接收插入的目标张量                                                     |\n"
"| `sub`       | `tensor`    | 要插入的子张量，其形状必须与`sizes`参数指定的形状匹配                                                        |\n"
"| `offsets`     | `tuple of ints`    | 指定在`ful`张量中插入的起始偏移量（每个维度） |\n"
"| `sizes` | `tuple of ints` | 指定插入区域的大小（每个维度）                                             |\n"
"| `strides` | `tuple of ints` | 指定插入区域的步长（每个维度）                                            |\n"
"| `_builder` |- | 保留参数，暂不支持外部调用                                            |\n"
"| `_generator`   | -               | 保留参数，暂不支持外部调用                                                |\n"
msgstr ""
"| Parameter Name | Type | Description |\n"
"| ------------- | ----------------- | -------------------------------------------------------------- |\n"
"| `ful` | `tensor` | The target tensor to receive the insertion |\n"
"| `sub` | `tensor` | The sub-tensor to be inserted, whose shape must match the shape specified by the `sizes` parameter |\n"
"| `offsets` | `tuple of ints` | Specifies the starting offsets (per dimension) for insertion into the `ful` tensor |\n"
"| `sizes` | `tuple of ints` | Specifies the size of the insertion region (per dimension) |\n"
"| `strides` | `tuple of ints` | Specifies the stride of the insertion region (per dimension) |\n"
"| `_builder` | - | Reserved parameter, external calls not supported for now |\n"
"| `_generator` | - | Reserved parameter, external calls not supported for now |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/insert_slice.md:14
msgid ""
"返回值：\n"
"`tensor`：插入子张量后的新张量\n"
msgstr ""
"Return value:  \n"
"`tensor`: a new tensor after inserting the sub-tensor\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/insert_slice.md:16
msgid "### 2.2 支持规格"
msgstr "### 2.2 Supported Specifications"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/insert_slice.md:18
msgid "#### 2.2.1 DataType 支持"
msgstr "#### 2.2.1 DataType Support"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/insert_slice.md:20
msgid ""
"|        | int8 | int16 | int32 | uint8 | uint16 | uint32 | uint64 | int64 | fp16 | fp32 | bf16 | bool |\n"
"| ------ | ---- | ----- | ----- | ----- | ------ | ------ | ------ | ----- | ---- | ---- | ---- | ---- |\n"
"| Ascend A2/A3 | √    | √     | √     | √     | √     | √       | √         |  √       | √    | √    |  √    | ×    |\n"
msgstr ""
"|        | int8 | int16 | int32 | uint8 | uint16 | uint32 | uint64 | int64 | fp16 | fp32 | bf16 | bool |\n"
