"| Ascend A2/A3 | √    | √     | √     | √     | √     | √       | √         |  √       | √    | √    |  √    | ×    |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/insert_slice.md:22
msgid "#### 2.2.2 Shape 支持"
msgstr "#### 2.2.2 Shape Support"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/insert_slice.md:24
msgid "支持任意形状的张量，但需满足："
msgstr "Supports tensors of arbitrary shapes, provided that:"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/insert_slice.md:26
msgid ""
"1. `ful`和`sub`的维度数必须相同\n"
"2. `offsets`、`sizes`、`strides`的长度必须与张量维度数相同\n"
"3. 插入区域不能超出`ful`张量的边界\n"
msgstr ""
"1. The number of dimensions of `ful` and `sub` must be the same.\n"
"2. The lengths of `offsets`, `sizes`, and `strides` must be the same as the number of tensor dimensions.\n"
"3. The insertion region must not exceed the boundaries of the `ful` tensor.\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/insert_slice.md:28
msgid "### 2.3 特殊限制说明"
msgstr "### 2.3 Special Limitations Explanation"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/insert_slice.md:30
msgid "无特殊限制"
msgstr "No special restrictions"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/insert_slice.md:32
msgid "### 2.4 使用方法"
msgstr "### 2.4 Usage"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/insert_slice.md:34
msgid "以下示例实现了将切片计算结果插入回原张量："
msgstr "The following example demonstrates inserting the slice computation result back into the original tensor:"

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/insert_slice.md:36
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"@triton.jit\n"
"def triton_kernel(x_ptr, y_ptr, output_ptr, n_elements, BLOCK_SIZE: tl.constexpr, SLICE_OFFSET: tl.constexpr, SLICE_SIZE: tl.constexpr):\n"
"    pid = tl.program_id(axis=0)\n"
"    block_start = pid * BLOCK_SIZE\n"
"    offsets = block_start + tl.arange(0, BLOCK_SIZE)\n"
"    mask = offsets < n_elements\n"
"    x = tl.load(x_ptr + offsets, mask=mask)\n"
"    y = tl.load(y_ptr + offsets, mask=mask)\n"
"    # 提取切片\n"
"    x_sub = tl.extract_slice(x, [block_start+SLICE_OFFSET], [SLICE_SIZE], [1])\n"
"    y_sub = tl.extract_slice(y, [block_start+SLICE_OFFSET], [SLICE_SIZE], [1])\n"
"    output_sub = x_sub + y_sub\n"
"    # 加载原始输出张量\n"
"    output = tl.load(output_ptr + offsets, mask=mask)\n"
"    # 将计算结果插入回原张量\n"
"    output = tl.insert_slice(output, output_sub, [block_start+SLICE_OFFSET], [SLICE_SIZE], [1])\n"
"    tl.store(output_ptr + offsets, output, mask=mask)\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

